description:
Bad things are brewing in the halls of the Ben Turpin School. When a science project goes awry, only the prepubescent children are spared the fate of zombification - which is not to say that they're immune from being eaten alive! George Romero covered night, dawn and day, but how about recess? With Recess Pieces, Bob Fingerman (Beg the Question, Minimum Wage) dishes up a grisly combination of Hal Roach's "Our Gang" and zombies, zombies and more zombies.

[Extract from Back Cover]
name: Recess Pieces
